SUMMARY:Free Watch Party: Quarterfinals Day 2
DESCRIPTION:Yesterday\, someone’s dream ended. Tonight\, two more teams leave everything on the pitch for a chance to write their name in World Cup history. We’ll be watching — will you? \nKickoff is at 2:00 p.m. Admission is free! \nCommunity Partner: We are proud to be joined by our Community Partner\, Dynamo & Dash Charities\, for this event! By leveraging the passion of players\, staff\, and fans\, Dynamo & Dash Charities provides resources and education to positively impact lives in the community. Stop by the Community Partner Booth to support their amazing work and learn more about their initiatives. \nAll food & beverage sale proceeds from the Community Partner booth will support Dynamo & Dash Charities and Levy Park. \nFood and Beverage Concessions: Enjoy a variety of festival food fare\, beer and wine\, and non-alcoholic beverages from Coca-Cola. \nMerchandise: Event merchandise celebrating Houston\, Levy Park\, and the global soccer tournament will also be available for purchase. \nArt Installations and Photo Opportunities: Commemorate the experience with a photo tour of the park\, including life-sized soccer-themed photo backdrops and a tournament bracket. Visit our soccer ball music box and turn the crank for festive sounds.
URL:https://www.levyparkhouston.org/events/quarterfinals-day-2/
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://www.levyparkhouston.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/2026-07.0910_Web-Graphic_Placeholder.jpg
END:VEVENT
