UID:10017854-1783706400-1783717200@www.levyparkhouston.org
SUMMARY:Sunset Bingo at Levy Park
DESCRIPTION:Bring your crew the second Friday of each month for a fun evening where you can take home fantastic prizes. Set to the backdrop of soulful tunes from DJ Del Sur\, Sunset Bingo is a great way to unwind and support Levy Park. All event proceeds directly support the park’s operations and programming. Please note: While children (and pups) can play\, an adult (18+) must be present to claim a prize. \n$10 for 8 games; $1 daubers are available for purchase\, or BYODauber (bring your own dauber). CASH ONLY \nEvent Schedule:\n6 p.m. – Board Sales Begin\n7 p.m. – Games Begin \nFood & Beverage Concessions: Enjoy convenient counter service with easy-to-eat\, handheld favorites like tortas\, flautas\, hot dogs\, and tacos at Gaspachos Mexican Bites—plus special treats for your four-legged friends! Hearsay is also serving up its eclectic cuisine\, refreshing cocktails\, and treats for your pup. Kind Ice Cream offers a 10% discount during games\, allowing Bingo participants to enjoy its irresistible selection of cakes and ice cream treats. Outside alcohol is not permitted but may be purchased from park concessionaires. \nNo outside furniture is allowed. Park furniture will be available\, or guests may bring a blanket for lawn seating. \nParking\nParking is available adjacent to the park and along Eastside Street and Wakeforest Avenue. Additional public parking (parking rate applies) is available in the Kirby Grove parking garage located on the corner of Richmond and Wakeforest. \nPlease note: Prizes and sponsors may vary by event. If you would like to donate an in-kind prize or sponsor Sunset Bingo\, please contact us at info@levyparkhouston.org. \n 
URL:https://www.levyparkhouston.org/events/sunset-bingo-at-levy-park/
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://www.levyparkhouston.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/IMG_6110-Edited-scaled.jpg
END:VEVENT
