SUMMARY:Houston Grand Opera- Storybook Opera
DESCRIPTION:Storytelling like you’ve never heard it before takes center stage as an opera singer presents an engaging and enjoyable introduction to opera for students. This program features singing storytellers for 30 minutes of captivating fun! \n4/4 – Lula the Mighty Griot \n5/2 – Eyes That Meet at the Corner \n6/6 – Goldilocks and the 3 Bears \n7/11 – World Cup Women \n9/5 – TBD \n10/3 – TBD \n11/7 –  TBD \n12/5 – TBD \n 
