SUMMARY:Dance and Move with Young Audiences of Houston
DESCRIPTION:Participants will learn to combine elements in dance\, music\, and theatre while expressing themselves through creative movement. We will use the fundamentals of dance to focus on story-telling while building skills in self-awareness\, social awareness\, relationship skills\, and responsible decision making.
